{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"position","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/position","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath 참고 문서</a></b>: <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 요소</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 함수</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 축</a>\n</div><p></p>\n<p><br>\n <code>position</code> 함수는 식 평가 문맥(expression evaluation context)와 위치가 같은 숫자를 반환합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ea.b5.ac.eb.ac.b8","title":"구문","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">position()\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".eb.b0.98.ed.99.98","title":"반환","isH3":true,"content":"<p>식 평가 문맥과 위치가 같은 정수.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.a3.bc.ec.9d.98","title":"주의","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>문맥 안 노드의 위치는 0 기반이 아님을 주의하세요. 첫 노드는 위치가 1입니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n <li>문맥은 경로의 나머지로 결정됩니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">&lt;xsl:template match=\"//a[position() = 5\"&gt;\n &lt;!-- 이 템플릿은 문서 안 다섯 번째 a 요소와 일치합니다. --&gt;\n&lt;/xsl:template&gt;\n</pre>\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">&lt;xsl:template match=\"//div[@class='foo']/bar[position() = 1]\"&gt;\n &lt;!-- 이 템플릿은 class 속성이 \"foo\"이고 div 요소의 자식인 첫 번째 bar 요소와 일치합니다 --&gt;\n&lt;/xsl:template&gt;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.a0.95.ec.9d.98","title":"정의","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#function-position\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.1</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_.ec.a7.80.ec.9b.90","title":"Gecko 지원","isH3":true,"content":"<p>지원함.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"position 함수는 식 평가 문맥(expression evaluation context)와 위치가 같은 숫자를 반환합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"position","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"position","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"position","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"position","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/xpath/functions/position","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/xpath/functions/position/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Functions"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/position","title":"position"}],"pageTitle":"position - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}